{
  "info": {
    "name": "Factory Flow ERP API",
    "description": "## Setup (required)\n\n1. **Seed the database** (from `backend/`): `node seeder.js` — creates users and sample data. *This wipes existing employees/products.*\n2. **Start API**: `npm start` in `backend/` (default **http://localhost:5000**).\n3. **Login** below uses **seeded** credentials. Change body if you use different users.\n\n## Auth\nRun **Auth → Login (seeded Admin)** first. Test script saves `token` to collection + environment.\n\n**`baseUrl`** must be the API origin only: `http://localhost:5000` — **not** `.../api`.\n\nOther requests use `Authorization: Bearer {{token}}`.\n\n## Seeded logins (password: `password123`)\n| Email | Role |\n|-------|------|\n| admin@integracnc.com | Admin |\n| finance@integracnc.com | finance_head |\n| hr@integracnc.com | hr_head |\n| employee@integracnc.com | employee |\n| buyer@integracnc.com | purchasing_head |\n| warehouse@integracnc.com | warehouse_head |\n\nOr **employeeId**: `EMP-001` … `EMP-006` with same password.\n\nReplace Mongo `_id` placeholders in URLs after listing resources.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:5000" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "productId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "clientId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "orderId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "poId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "vendorId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "vendorBillId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "shipmentId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "invoiceMongoId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "approvalId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "employeeId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "savedViewId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "reservationId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "notificationId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "jobId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "bomId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "platformTenantId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "platformEmployeeId", "value": "" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (seeded Admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (j.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', j.token);",
                  "    try { pm.environment.set('token', j.token); } catch (e) {}",
                  "    console.log('Token saved (collection + env if active).');",
                  "  }",
                  "} else {",
                  "  try { console.log('Login failed:', pm.response.json()); } catch (e) {}",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@integracnc.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
            "description": "After `node seeder.js`. Or: `\"employeeId\": \"EMP-001\"` + same password. Other roles: see collection description."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Purchasing — PO routes)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (j.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', j.token);",
                  "    try { pm.environment.set('token', j.token); } catch (e) {}",
                  "  }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"buyer@integracnc.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Warehouse — shipments)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
